    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BLANKS®\nCONFIRMATION OF TELEGRAM FROM\nTHE STATE NATIONAL BANK\nST. LOUIS, MO.\nSt Louis Mo\nMarch 18 1927\nChas A Lindbergh\nU S Grant Hotel\nSan Diego\nCalifornia\nScott offered whirlwind motor owned by In B Hunt twenty one hundred\ndollars fob Moneta California\nMotor represented completely\noverhauled and includes eight extra cylinders propeller ete\nDont\nknow how many hours motor has had or what condition it is in\nyou run over to Moneta and give us your judgment on price\nCould\nH M Bixby\nState National Bank\nPaid-charge\nState National Bank"
